---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - Aakriti Mehndi Artist" description="Terms and Conditions for booking Aakriti Mehndi Artist">
  <div class="py-24 bg-surface min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:font-normal prose-p:font-body prose-p:font-light prose-p:text-ink-muted">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-ink mb-8">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">1. Booking and Payments</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">A token advance payment is required to confirm all bookings. The remaining balance must be paid on the day of the event prior to the completion of the service. Travel charges, if applicable, will be discussed and agreed upon during the consultation.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">2. Cancellations and Rescheduling</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Cancellations made 48 hours or more prior to the appointment will receive a full refund of the token amount. Cancellations made within 48 hours of the appointment will forfeit the token amount. You may reschedule your appointment once without penalty, subject to our availability.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">3. Preparation and Aftercare</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Clients are expected to have clean, lotion-free hands and feet prior to the application. We are not responsible for poor stain results due to failure to follow provided aftercare instructions or the use of chemical lotions prior to the appointment.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">4. Liability</h2>
      <p>We use natural henna paste. While allergic reactions are extremely rare with natural henna, clients with known sensitivities should request a patch test prior to application. We are not liable for any allergic reactions or medical complications that may arise.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
